{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775879567766,"sessionID":"ses_28556d22bffevyS1U2GDohG19W","part":{"id":"prt_d7aabb4a2001E8skcVXk8pL9Di","messageID":"msg_d7aab8658001RQnhFdsFxE3VB5","sessionID":"ses_28556d22bffevyS1U2GDohG19W","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller\n2: \n3: ## AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n4: \n5: | Field | Value |\n6: |-------|-------|\n7: | **Module** | `pkg/agentd` |\n8: | **Language** | Go |\n9: | **Size** | S (Small) |\n10: | **Status** | Proposed |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Purpose\n15: \n16: Implement the Agentd idle cleanup controller that automatically deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when they have been inactive beyond a configured timeout. This proposal delivers:\n17: \n18: 1. **Reconciler Controller**: A controller-runtime reconciler that watches `Sandbox` resources and manages their lifecycle based on activity timestamps\n19: 2. **Idle Detection**: Reading and parsing the `last-activity-time` annotation to determine when a sandbox was last active\n20: 3. **Automatic Cleanup**: Deleting sandboxes that have exceeded the `SessionExpirationTimeout` (15 minutes)\n21: 4. **Efficient Requeueing**: Scheduling reconciliation at the exact expiration time to minimize unnecessary API calls\n22: 5. **Error Handling**: Graceful handling of parse errors, not-found errors, and deletion failures\n23: 6. **Binary Integration**: A standalone `agentd` binary that runs the controller using controller-runtime manager\n24: \n25: This controller integrates with the agentcube platform to ensure sandboxes don't consume resources indefinitely when idle, complementing the workload manager's sandbox creation and session management capabilities.\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## Scope\n30: \n31: ### In Scope\n32: \n33: | Item | Detail |\n34: |------|--------|\n35: | **Reconciler** | controller-runtime `Reconciler` implementation for Sandbox resources |\n36: | **Idle Detection** | Reading `last-activity-time` annotation from Sandbox metadata |\n37: | **Time Parsing** | RFC3339 timestamp parsing with error handling |\n38: | **Expiration Logic** | Computing expiration time based on `SessionExpirationTimeout` |\n39: | **Resource Deletion** | Deleting Sandbox resources via Kubernetes client |\n40: | **Requeue Scheduling** | Smart requeue at expiration time for pending cleanups |\n41: | **Error Handling** | Proper handling of NotFound, parse errors, and delete errors |\n42: | **Manager Setup** | Controller-runtime manager configuration and startup |\n43: | **Scheme Registration** | Registration of Sandbox CRD types |\n44: | **Binary Entrypoint** | `cmd/agentd/main.go` with signal-driven shutdown |\n45: \n46: ### Out of Scope\n47: \n48: - Activity tracking/timestamp updates (handled by workload manager)\n49: - Custom idle timeout per sandbox (uses fixed 15-minute threshold)\n50: - Graceful shutdown of sandbox workloads before deletion\n51: - Cleanup of related Kubernetes resources (pods, secrets) - handled by ownerReferences\n52: - Metrics and monitoring endpoints\n53: - Leader election for multi-replica deployments\n54: - Webhook validation for Sandbox resources\n55: - Horizontal scaling considerations\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## Design\n60: \n61: ### File Structure\n62: \n63: | File | Role | Lines (est.) |\n64: |------|------|--------------|\n65: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler.go` | Reconciler implementation | ~100 |\n66: | `pkg/agentd/reconciler_test.go` | Unit tests for reconciler | ~150 |\n67: | `cmd/agentd/main.go` | Binary entrypoint | ~60 |\n68: \n69: ### Architecture\n70: \n71: ```\n72: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n73: │                    Kubernetes Cluster                    │\n74: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n75: │  │              Agentd Controller                   │    │\n76: │  │  ┌───────────────────────────────────────────┐  │    │\n77: │  │  │         Controller-Runtime Manager         │  │    │\n78: │  │  │  ┌─────────┐  ┌─────────┐  ┌───────────┐  │  │    │\n79: │  │  │  │  Watch  │──►│Reconcile│──►│  Delete   │  │  │    │\n80: │  │  │  │ Sandbox │  │         │  │  Sandbox  │  │  │    │\n81: │  │  │  └─────────┘  └────┬────┘  └───────────┘  │  │    │\n82: │  │  │                    │                      │  │    │\n83: │  │  │              ┌─────┴─────┐                │  │    │\n84: │  │  │              ▼           ▼                │  │    │\n85: │  │  │        ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐         │  │    │\n86: │  │  │        │Parse Time│  │Schedule  │         │  │    │\n87: │  │  │        │RFC3339   │  │Requeue   │         │  │    │\n88: │  │  │        └──────────┘  └──────────┘         │  │    │\n89: │  │  └───────────────────────────────────────────┘  │    │\n90: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n91: │                           │                              │\n92: │                           ▼                              │\n93: │  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │\n94: │  │            Sandbox CRD (agents.x-k8s.io)         │    │\n95: │  │  metadata:                                       │    │\n96: │  │    annotations:                                  │    │\n97: │  │      last-activity-time: \"2026-03-21T10:00:00Z\" │    │\n98: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │\n99: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n100: ```\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 550. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Proposal: Agentd Idle Cleanup Controller\n\n## AR-018 — Agentd 空闲清理控制器\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **Module** | `pkg/agentd` |\n| **Language** | Go |\n| **Size** | S (Small) |\n| **Status** | Proposed |\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\nImplement the Agentd idle cleanup controller that automatically deletes `Sandbox` custom resources when they have been inactive beyond a configured timeout. This proposal delivers:\n\n1. **Reconciler Controller**: A controller-runtime reconciler that watches `Sandbox` resources and manages their lifecycle based on activity timestamps\n2. **Idle Detection**: Reading and parsing the `last-activity-time` annotation to determine when a sandbox was last active\n3. **Automatic Cleanup**: Deleting sandboxes that have exceeded the `SessionExpirationTimeout` (15 minutes)","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775879567756,"end":1775879567764}}}}
